    ?.  |(=(nex hoon-version) =(+(nex) hoon-version))
      ::  XX revise hint
      ::
      ~>(%mean.'wyrd: vega:' !!)
    ::  require runtime compatibility
    ::
    %-  (wyrd kel [hoon/nex ~])
    ::
    ::  if we're upgrading language versions, recompile the compiler
